credit_line: Gift of the Estate of Dorothy (Liebes) Morin
dimensions: Warp x Weft: 20 x 15 cm (7 7/8 x 5 7/8 in.)
title: Sample
description: Derivation from 2/2 and 3/1 twill weave in shades of green with copper metallic yarns. Warp is green boucle paired with smooth yarn. Weft is a regular alternation of boucle, wrapped copper yarn, boucle, braided green yarn and wide plied green yarn. Weave gives the effect of horizontal ridges on the surface of the fabric.
name: Sample
